title: Pseudo Echo - Autumnal Park [New Wave 1984]
description:
There's no doubt that "Autumnal Park" was one of the catchiest but at the same time most overlooked new wave records of the 80's. 320kBS CD rip re-posted as per request as old torrent is dead.

Pseudo Echo is: Brian Canham, Pierre Pierre, Darren Danielson & Ben Grayson
